# Safety-first: ignore everything, then whitelist only what goes on GitHub.
# This prevents accidental pushes of student data, rosters, or readings.
*

# Allow git and project config
!.gitignore
!README.md
!PSCI3328.Rproj

# Syllabi
!syllabi/
!syllabi/**

# Slides: rendered outputs, sources, and assets
!slides/
!slides/*.pdf
!slides/*.qmd
!slides/*.html
!slides/*.scss
!slides/*_files/
!slides/*_files/**
!slides/pictures/
!slides/pictures/**

# Always ignore these even if they land in an allowed folder
.DS_Store
.Rhistory
